---------
Animated Profile Card UI design using html and css 

->Its is a responsive profile card

->At first, on the webpage, there is only an image with a round border-color. But when you hover on that card, then the height and width of the card smoothly expand and show the contents of the card.
 
->Animated Profile Card that you can use as an ID and can share with anyone. It contains links for your social media accounts, and a bit about yourself.

